<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ขอใช้ตู้เก็บของ</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .navbar {
            background-color: #3b5998 !important;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
        }
        .navbar-brand, .nav-link {
            color: #ffffff !important;
        }
        .card {
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #3b5998;
            border: none;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #2d4373;
        }
        .display-6 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .card {
            border: none;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
        }
        .card-body {
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #007bff;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .alert {
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('nav', { user: user, currentPage: 'locker' }) %>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="card shadow-sm col-md-8 mx-auto">
            <div class="card-body text-center">
                <h1 class="mb-4">ขอใช้ตู้เก็บของ</h1>
                <div class="alert alert-warning" role="alert">
                    <h4 class="alert-heading">กำลังพัฒนา</h4>
                    <p>ขออภัยในความไม่สะดวก ระบบนี้กำลังอยู่ในระหว่างการพัฒนา</p>
                    <hr>
                    <p class="mb-0">โปรดกลับมาใหม่ในภายหลัง</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
